a-image-sizes=3D"384 662 992 1920" src=3D"https://rbts.co/img/1f1387d4de101=
_1920.webp" style=3D"aspect-ratio: 4190 / 2200; cursor: zoom-in;"> <div sty=
le=3D"display:flex;box-sizing:border-box"> <div style=3D"margin:auto"> <h1 =
id=3D"c50m" style=3D"font-size:7em;font-weight:800;color:#fff;text-shadow:0=
 0 10px #000;line-height:1.15;font-variation-settings:'YTUC' 700">C50M</h1>=
 <span class=3D"subtitle" style=3D"font-size:1.9em;font-weight:400;text-sha=
dow:0 0 5px #000;margin-bottom:0">Camera Module for Raspberry Pi, Nvidia Je=
tson and Rockchip RK3588</span> </div> </div> </section> <section id=3D"the=
-c50m-camera-module"> <h2>The C50M Camera Module</h2> <div style=3D"display=
:flex"> <ul style=3D"column-count:2"> <li>50MP Photos</li> <li>8K 30 FPS Vi=
deo</li> <li>Huge 1/1.12" sensor with 1.4=CE=BCm pixels</li> <li>Wide-angle=
 (90=C2=B0), Auto-focus F1.8 lens</li> </ul> </div> </section> <section> <p=
>Experience the world from new heights and see the unseen in the minute det=
ails with our state-of-the-art C50M camera module equipped with the Samsung=
 ISOCELL GN2 image sensor (also powering the Google Pixel 8 Pro). This sens=
or is designed to deliver superior performance that is ideal for applicatio=
ns in drones, machine vision, industrial automation, and more.</p> <p>The C=
50M's 8K video recording capability takes aerial and machine vision to the =
next level. For drone enthusiasts, you can now capture everyday moments fro=
m the sky in incredible detail. For machine vision applications, this high =
resolution allows for more detailed data collection and image analysis, enh=
ancing the ability to identify objects or detect defects.</p> <p>The ISOCEL=
L GN2 sensor in the C50M camera module can take stunning 50MP photos, enabl=
ing drones to capture the world below in extraordinary detail. The high res=
olution also improves the accuracy of machine vision systems by allowing fo=
r more precise feature detection and identification.</p> <p>Don't let the d=
arkness limit your vision. The large 1.4=CE=BCm pixels of the ISOCELL GN2 s=
ensor provide impressive low-light performance, ensuring clear, bright imag=
es even in challenging lighting conditions, whether for drones flying in lo=
w-light environments or machine vision systems operating in dimly lit facto=
ries.</p> <p>Experience lightning-fast autofocus with the ISOCELL GN2 senso=
r. Its Dual Pixel Pro technology allows quick focus on any object, making i=
t ideal for drones tracking fast-moving objects and machine vision applicat=
ions where quick response times are critical.</p> <p>Our C50M camera module=
 with the ISOCELL GN2 sensor also features high dynamic range (HDR) capabil=
ities. This means your drone can capture vibrant photos even in mixed light=
ing conditions, and your machine vision systems can maintain clarity in con=
trasting light settings.</p> <p>Harness the power of the Samsung ISOCELL GN=
2 sensor with our C50M camera module to unlock new possibilities in your dr=
one and machine vision applications.</p> <figure> <img alt=3D"C50M with Ras=
pberry Pi 4 for scale" data-image-id=3D"48b38ac6047c3" data-image-sizes=3D"=
384 662 992 1920" src=3D"https://rbts.co/img/48b38ac6047c3_384.webp" style=
=3D"aspect-ratio: 8936 / 6345; cursor: zoom-in;"> <figcaption>Raspberry Pi =
4 B for scale</figcaption> </figure> </section> <section id=3D"specificatio=
