r lane) D-PHY, I2C, frame-sync output</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Chroma</td> <td>T=
etra</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Auto Focus</td> <td>Dual Pixel Pro (PDAF)</td> </t=
r> <tr> <td>WDR</td> <td>Smart-ISO Pro (iDCG), Staggered HDR</td> </tr> <tr=
